@startuml
title Sequence - Ontology Module

actor "Extraction/Graph consumer" as C
participant "taxonomy.py" as TAX
participant "CAMEO/GDELT taxonomy" as CAMEO
participant "IPTC topics" as IPTC
participant "OWL-Time concepts" as OWLT
participant "event_extractor.py" as EVT
participant "relation_extractor.py" as REL
participant "graph_loader.py" as LOAD
participant "competency_queries.py" as CQ

C -> TAX : map event/relation semantics
TAX -> CAMEO : resolve event class
TAX -> IPTC : resolve topic labels
TAX -> OWLT : resolve temporal semantics
TAX --> C : normalized ontology mapping

C -> EVT : apply mapped event categories
C -> REL : apply mapped relation classes
C -> LOAD : materialize graph labels/types
C -> CQ : align query filters and facets

@enduml
